Mai magana da yawun Taliban a farkon makon nan ya ce a shirye su ke da su tattauna da shugabannin Kabul bayan hutun bikin Sallar Layya a karshen watan nan, idan an kammala batun musayar firsunoni.
Babbar damuwar Pakistan shine kasancewar mayakan Afghanistan, musanmman wandada ke da alaka da 'yan TTP ko kuma Jama'at-ul-Ahrar ko kuma Lashkar-e-Islam, da kuma wadanda suke tare da sojojin kwatar 'yancin Baluschistan, wadanta dauki alhakkin manya-manyan hare-haren da aka kai kudancin lardin Sindh da kuma kudu maso yammacin lardin Baluschistan a watan nan.
An hallaka yawacin jami'an soji a wannan wata a kudu maso yammacin lardin Baluchistan a wani yaki da 'yan tada kayar bayan.
Kungiyar TTP ce ta dauki alhakkin kai harin mafi muni a Pakistan a shekarar 2014, yayin da aka kai hari a wata makarantar sojoji aka kuma kashe mutane 140.
