Daya daga cikin manyan bankunan Birtaniya HSBC ya musanta "shirya gadar zare" ga kamfanin Huawei na China cikin binciken da Amurka take yi - Labaran Kasuwanci na RT
Landan- Babban Shalkwatar bankin HSBC na kasa da kasa ya bayyana a kafofin sada zumunta cewa kamar yadda kafofin watsa labaran China su ka yi "Ikirarin shaida" a kan Huawei ba haka bane, inda abin ya kai ga kama babban jami'in kudin kamfanin na Canada.
Cikin wani sako na WeChat wanda yanzu ba'a samu, mai bayar da rancen ya ce aiyukan da ta yi ba su suka haifar da binciken da Amurka take yiwa babban kamfanin samar da kayayyakin sadarwa na duniya ba, illa bincikar kamfanin kan zargin watsi da takunkumin da Amurka ta sanyawa Iran akan Huawei ya fara tun kafin bankin ya shigo cikin karshen a shekarar 2016.
A ranar Asabar bankin na mai cewa, "HSBC ba ta da wata kiyayya dangane da Huawei kuma ba ta shiryawa Huawei "gadar zare ba," ya kara da cewa ba zai taba boye gaskiyar ba daganne da abokan huldarsa ba.
"Duba da bukatar US DOJ [Ma'aikatar Shari'a ta Amurka na neman bayani, gungun kamfanin HSBC cikin sauki ya gabatar da gaskiyar manufar kawai ce kawai.
HSBC ba ta "kirkiri" shaida ko kuma "boye" gaskiya ba."
A rt.com kuma yunkurin Birtaniya na haramtawa kamfanin Huawei fito da fasahar sadarwa ta 5G ya nuna tasirin Amurka a kan manufofin kasashen waje na Birtaniya - George Galloway ga Boom Bust
An toshe sakon a shafin a dandalin tare da bayanin cewa "ya sabawa ka'idoji" yanzu kuma babu shi.
Wannan bayanin ya fito ne bayan da kafofin yada labarai na China da suka hada da jaridun dake da alaka da gwamati suka zargi HSBC da "kitsa" makarkashiya tare da Washington don kulla wa Huawei gadar zare.
Kamfanin ya fada tsakiyar rikicin badkala ta diflomasiya na tsawon shekara daya da rabi tun da aka tsare Meng Wanzhou, wani babban Jami'in Hada-hadar kudi a watan Disamba ta shekarar 2018 a Canada daga wata takardar sammaci daga Amurka.
Meng yana fuskantar tuhuma a kan zargin yin amfani da kamfanin shell don karya takunkumin da aka sa wa Iran da kuma zargin yiwa bankuna karya dangane da alakar da ke tsakanin kamafanin Huawei da kamfanin Iran Skycom.
A cewar wata sabuwar shaidar da Global Times ta fitar, HSBC tana sane sarai da mu'malar kamfanin na China da Skycom.
Bankin a cewar rahoton ya zabi ya "hada kai" da gwamantin Amurka don gujewa hukunci mai tsanani a shekarar 2012, a lokacin da bankin ya amsa laifin shigar da kudaden haram da ya karya takunkumin wanda ya kunshi cuzgunawa Iran.
An umarci Bankin da a lokacin da ya biya tara ta kusan dala biliyan 1.9 ya kuma gujewa duk wata dabi'a irin wannan.
"Hujja ta nuna cewa HSBC ta fahimci wannan dangantakar amma da gangan ta sayar da takardun bayanan sirrin abokan mu'amalarta ga bangaren Amurka domin gwamnatin Amurka su iya kawar da kai ga rashin da'ar bankin Birtaniya kuma ba a hukunta shi ba a karkashin Yarjejeniyar da aka Kaddamar ta Laifuka," labarin da jaridar ta bayyana a daya daga cikin rubuce-rubcenta game da batun.
A wani gargadi na harbin iska, jaridar da ke karkashin ikon fadar Beijing ta kara da cewa idan aka tabbatar da laifin mai bayar da rancen na "hada baki" zai iya fuskantar "hukunci mai tsanani" a China, daya daga cikin manyan kasuwannin HSBC.
Wannan ba shine karon farko ba da a ka sa bankin a gaba a 'yan makonnin nan.
A watan da ya wuce, an yiwa HSBC kaca-kaca a saboda goyon baya waata sabuwar dokar tsaron kasa na Hong Kong, a garin da kasuwancin ya samo asali kuma yake da fiye da rabin ribarsa.
Bankin ya sha caccaka daga bangarori biyu - daga Yammaci, tare da Mike Pompeo Sakataren Kula da Harkokin Wajen Amurka ya kira tallafawar da zama "kamafanin dan amshin shata," sai kuma Gabas, tare da bangaren China aka rawaito suna cewa tallafinsu "yayi jinkiri"
