SEATTLE - Bayan makonni da aka diba ana gwabzawa tsakanin masu zanga-zanga da hukumomin tarayya na Portland, Ore dandazon mutane kimanin 2,000 sunyi taru a Seattle a ranar Asabar, suna kutsawa kan tituna a yayin da suke arangama da yan sanda.
An jikkata jami'an yan sanda uku, an kwantar da daya a asibiti dauke da rauni a kafa sanadiyar abun fashewa, an kuma kame masu tarzoma 16 da la'asar, kamar yadda yan sanda suka bayyana.
Suna dauke da rubuce-rubuce irinsu "Yan tarayya a Koma Gida" sannan suna ihun cewa "Babu adalci, babu zaman lafiya." masu tarzomar sun tsatstsaya a gurin da za'a dinga daure matasa anan gaba sun kuma ciccinnawa gine-ginen dake gurin wuta.
Wasu kuma sun farfasa windunan shagunan kasuwancin dake kusa.
Yan sanda sunyi fito na fito da dandazon mutanen a unguwar Capitol Hill, inda suka dinga jefa gurneti mai kashe idanu da feshin barkono kafin su fara diban mutane suna tsarewa.
Bipasha Mukherjee, mai shekaru 52 yar Kirkiland, Wash, tace tun watan Mayu take zanga-zanga akan tituna sai dai kuma tace ta shiga damuwa ganin irin wannan mummunan hanyar da yan sanda suka dauka.
"Ba haka kasar da nayo hjira na dawo take ba," Inji Malama Mukherjee, wacce tazo daga kasar Indiya sama da shekaru 30 da suka shude.
"Sai nake ji a raina kamar kasarmu tana komawa ta kama karya kuma amfani da karfin ikon yan sanda."
Michaud Savage daga Seattle yace ana zanga-zangar ne don nuna kyama ga kananan hukumomi da kuma jami'an tarayya da aka kawo domin kawo karshen tarzomar da taki karewa a Portland.
Mista Savage yace hanyoyin da jami'an tsaro suke amfani da su a Portland, wanda ya hada da yin amfani barkonon tsohuwa da kuma alburushin roba, suna da hatsari kuma bai dace ba.
"Abu ne mai ciwo sosai kuma ya wuce gona da iri," Inji Mista Savage a yayin da yake wanke idanunsa saboda feshin barkono da kuma raunin dake hancinsa da dantsen hannunsa sanadiyar gurneti mai gusar da gani.
Mutuwar George Floyd a hannun yan sanda dake Minneapolis cikin watan Mayu shi ya haifar da zanga-zangar da ta jawo miliyoyin mutane kan tituna dake birane daban-daban, sai dai zanga-zangar ta ragu a yawancin birane.
Duk da haka zangar-zangar Seattle da Portland ci gaba tayi da karuwa.
Masu zanga-zangar Seattle a wani lokaci sun taba bayyana wasu gine-gine da yawa dake unguwar Capitol Hill sun kuma yi ikirarin mayar da yankin mai cin gashin kansa.
Bayan harbe-harbe a gurin yan sanda suka share gurin, zanga-zangar ta lafa.
A halin yanzu ana ci gaba da zanga-zanga a Portland inda tarzomar tafi muni a kusa da gine-ginen tarayya dake cikin birnin.
Bayan Shugaban kasa Trump ya bayar da umarnin zartarwa don a kare mutun-mutumi da kuma dukiyoyin tarayya, sai Hukumar Tsaron cikin Gida ta girke tawagar jami'ai a cikin brnin, wanda suka fara haifar jerin rikice-rikice wanda ya jikkata masu zanga-zangar, babban insifekta janar na bincike yayi kira ga shuwagabbin cikin gida akan jami'an tarayya su janye.
Dandazon masu zanga-zangar sun ninka zuwa dubunnai, sannan kuma ana ci gaba da yin tarzomar a can.
Hukumar tarayya ta girke jami'anta a Seattle cikin wannan makon, inda masu zanga-zangar suka bayyna hakan a matsayin daya daga cikin dalilan yin zanga-zangar a ranar Asabar.
