Babar Xerxes da aka yiwa mutuwa, sarauniya Atossa (Lydia Koniordou), a cikin wata babbar doguwar riga da ta fito da ramarta, maimakon baya; mutum ce amma kwarangwal a cikin kaya, gaba daya cikin rauni da taurin rai.
Koniordu, wanda ke cikin 'yan wasan kwaikwayo na dabe na Girka mafi shara, a ta san rawar da zata taka cike da waje - ita ta bayar da umarni ta kuma fito a shirin kungiyar wasan kwaikwayo na kasa ta Girka a wasan na "Farisawa" da aka yi cibiyar wasanni na New York a shekarar 2006 - kuma ita ce ta jagoranci tafiy ba tare da cikin sauki, kamar ba ta yi aikin komai ba.
